    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single below-required factor (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) is accepted on the basis that ASTM F1717 specifies a single standardized load configuration and no additional conditions are clinically indicated for this device class. Overall credibility is sufficient for Medium model risk at Class II device level.",
